<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Coal Work Service</title>

    <!-- css file link  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/media.css">

    <!-- bootstrap cdn link  -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- remix icon cdn  -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css"
    rel="stylesheet"/>
    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <!-- font family use  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
  <main>
    <article>
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="coal-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Professional Coal Work Services</h2>
              <p class="lead mb-4">We provide comprehensive coal mining, handling, and transportation solutions with a focus on safety, efficiency, and environmental responsibility.</p>
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-dark px-4 py-2">Contact Us</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
              <figure>
                <img src="img/Coal work.jpg" alt="Coal Mining" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
              </figure>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Services Section -->
      <section class="coal-section pt-0">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row center-title mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
              <h2 class="section-title">Our Coal Services</h2>
              <p class="text-muted">Comprehensive solutions for all your coal-related needs</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-truck-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Coal Transportation</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Safe and timely transportation of coal with a strong logistics network and well-maintained fleet of vehicles.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Fleet of 50+ heavy-duty trucks</li>
                  <li>GPS tracking for real-time monitoring</li>
                  <li>Adherence to all safety regulations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-community-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Coal Mining</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Efficient mining operations with a focus on safety, productivity, and environmental responsibility.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Modern mining equipment</li>
                  <li>Expert mining engineers</li>
                  <li>Environmental impact assessment</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-settings-3-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Coal Handling</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Streamlined coal loading, unloading, and storage facilities for smooth industrial supply chain management.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Mechanical handling systems</li>
                  <li>Dust control measures</li>
                  <li>Quality control processes</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-flask-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Coal Quality Testing</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Comprehensive quality analysis and testing services to ensure coal meets industry standards.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Calorific value testing</li>
                  <li>Moisture content analysis</li>
                  <li>Ash content measurement</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-leaf-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Environmental Solutions</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Eco-friendly practices and solutions to minimize environmental impact of coal operations.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Dust suppression systems</li>
                  <li>Water management solutions</li>
                  <li>Land reclamation services</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card service-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                <i class="ri-customer-service-2-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Consultation Services</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Expert consultation for coal mining projects, logistics planning, and operational efficiency.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3 ps-3">
                  <li>Project feasibility studies</li>
                  <li>Operational efficiency audits</li>
                  <li>Regulatory compliance guidance</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <section class="coal-section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row center-title mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
              <h2 class="section-title">Our Working Process</h2>
              <p class="text-muted">A systematic approach to ensure quality and efficiency</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Needs Assessment</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">We begin by understanding your specific requirements and challenges.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Planning</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Our experts develop a detailed plan tailored to your needs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Execution</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">We implement the plan with precision and attention to detail.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="process-step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold">Quality Assurance</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Rigorous quality checks ensure the highest standards are met.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Safety Section -->
      <section class="safety-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row center-title mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
              <h2 class="section-title text-white">Safety & Environmental Commitment</h2>
              <p>We prioritize safety and environmental responsibility in all our operations</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="bg-white rounded p-4 text-center h-100">
                <i class="ri-shield-check-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-black">Safety First Approach</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Rigorous safety protocols and continuous training ensure the well-being of our workforce and communities.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3">
                  <li>Regular safety audits and inspections</li>
                  <li>Personal protective equipment mandates</li>
                  <li>Emergency response preparedness</li>
                  <li>Safety training programs</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="bg-white rounded p-4 text-center h-100">
                <i class="ri-earth-line coal-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-black">Environmental Stewardship</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">We implement sustainable practices to minimize our environmental footprint and protect natural resources.</p>
                <ul class="text-start text-muted mt-3">
                  <li>Dust and emission control systems</li>
                  <li>Water conservation and management</li>
                  <li>Land rehabilitation programs</li>
                  <li>Waste reduction initiatives</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
  <%- include('footer.ejs') %>
  <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>